163
00:09:18,309 --> 00:09:23,197
how we can burn tritium efficiently,
and the thermo-dynamical efficiency

164
00:09:23,197 --> 00:09:27,081
of the reactor itself, for example,
giving some constraints

165
00:09:27,081 --> 00:09:30,667
on the operational temperatures 
for the reactor and so on, and so forth.

166
00:09:31,255 --> 00:09:34,357
These are many, many elements 
that one needs to look at

167
00:09:34,357 --> 00:09:38,859
for a burning plasma and for a reactor
to be compatible with burning plasma.

