409
00:24:08,444 --> 00:24:13,881
Resonanr de-stabilization that occurs
because the mode frequency coincides

410
00:24:13,881 --> 00:24:16,414
with the precession frequency
for the fast ions.

411
00:24:17,154 --> 00:24:21,236
And the precession frequency is what 
we have described just two minutes ago.

412
00:24:22,995 --> 00:24:25,951
The point is that this kind of modes
is driven by the fast ions

413
00:24:25,951 --> 00:24:28,852
but in turn can reach amplitudes
